 Features
✅ User Authentication (Signup, Login, Logout)
✅ Upload & Watch Videos
✅ Like & Dislike Videos
✅ Comment on Videos (Add, Edit, Delete)
✅ Search Videos
✅ View User Profiles & Channels
✅ Fully Responsive UI

 Tech Stack-----------------------------
Frontend (React + Tailwind CSS)
React Router - Navigation
Axios - API Requests
Tailwind CSS - Styling
Toastify - Notifications
MUI Icons - Icons
Backend (Node.js + Express)
MongoDB + Mongoose - Database
JWT Authentication - Security
Cloudinary - Media Uploads
Bcrypt - Password Hashing



Setup Instructions--------------------


cd ourtube

 Backend Setup------------------

Navigate to the Backend Directory

cd server
Install Dependencies

npm install
Create a .env File
Inside server/, create a .env file and add:

PORT=4000
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
CLIENT_URL=string_path

Before starting the server , initiazine DB with node init.js
this will create demo Data for App

Start the Backend Server----------

npm run dev
Your backend should now be running on http://localhost:4000/ 

Frontend Setup-------------------
Navigate to the Frontend Directory

cd client
Install Dependencies
npm install

Start the React App
npm start

Your frontend should now be running now

Usage ---------------
Sign Up / Log In to access features.
Upload Videos with title, description & thumbnail.
Watch Videos and interact using likes & comments.
Search for Videos and browse user channels.

githubLink :-  https://github.com/doabletome/OurTube.git